thread.title: Whitehaven defensive back Donte Vaughn commits to Notre Dame
thread.title_full: Whitehaven defensive back Donte Vaughn commits to Notre Dame

author: John Varlas
title: Whitehaven defensive back Donte Vaughn commits to Notre Dame
text:
Whitehaven standout defensive back Donte Vaughn announced today that he has verbally committed to Notre Dame.
The 6-3, 195-pounder is ranked as the seventh-best prospect in the state and the No. 18 safety nationally by Rivals.com. Vaughn had offers from 14 other schools, including Auburn, LSU, Mississippi State, Ole Miss and Tennessee.
Verbal commitments are nonbinding but Vaughn is expected to make it official on National Signing Day in February.
